 <section_number>12-2155</section_number>
 <catch_line>DECLARATION OF NECESSITY.</catch_line>
 <order_by>12-2155</order_by>
 <text>
  <section prefix="(a)">	Reduce the likelihood that these residential housing accommodations will become public nuisances in violation of G.S. 19-1(b). 
</section>
  <section prefix="(b)">	Promote responsible management of these housing accommodations.
</section>
  <section prefix="(c)">	Assist in providing a safe habitat for residents and neighbors of these facilities.
</section>
  <section prefix="(d)">	Safeguard property values. 
(Ord. No. 1992-31, ยง1, 8-4-92) 
</section>
